    "body": "## Problem\r\nRanges represented by marks are usually end-inclusive, but the range utilities we provided are end-exclusive.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nAdd pos:to_mark(), pos.mark(), range:to_mark(), and range.mark().\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-05-18T14:45:21Z",
    "comment_data": [
